shell.go
    shell
        Navigate across buttons / input with tab / btab
        selectively disable buttons based on context
            ~ only when Hold and Door states
            ! only with Idle, Run, Jog states
            0x85 jog cancel only for Jog state
            0x9E spindle stop only on Hold state
            0xA0 flood coolant only on Idle, Run or Hold states.
            0x45 mist coolang only on Idle, Run or Hold states.
        fix
            omit $G and $G for
                M0
                feed hold
            don't wait for response for M0
        Alarm state should cancel send command context
        Send File
        Grbl
            View build info ($I)
            Jogging
                Jogging ($J=*)
                Jog Cancel (0x85)
            Overrides
                Feed
                    Set 100% of programmed rate. (0x90)
                    Increase 10% (0x91)
                    Decrease 10% (0x92)
                    Increase 1% (0x93)
                    Decrease 1% (0x94)
                Rapid
                    Set to 100% full rapid rate. (0x95)
                    Set to 50% of rapid rate. (0x96)
                    Set to 25% of rapid rate. (0x97)
                Spindle Speed
                    Set 100% of programmed spindle speed (0x99)
                    Increase 10% (0x9A)
                    Decrease 10% (0x9B)
                    Increase 1% (0x9C)
                    Decrease 1% (0x9D)
            Settings
                Settings ($$, $x=val)
                Startup Blocks ($N, $Nx=)
                Restore Grbl settings and data to defaults ($RST=$, $RST=#, $RST=*)
        Scripting
            https://github.com/google/starlark-go
            https://github.com/d5/tengo
        Log handling
            use ANSI escape functions
    grbl
        implement stream
        fix
            when sendCommand times out before response message comes, it is discarded
